Package msvc.exceptions

package msvc.exceptions
Contains classes related to the 32-bit exception handling data structures created by Microsoft Visual C++.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    msvc.exceptions.code
    Contains helper classes for finding function prologues matching how Microsoft Visual C++ (MSVC) creates these when exception handling (EH) is in play, and for matching code that registers the MSVC EH entry data structure (with optional security cookie-checking code before that).
